{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/technical/2020-07-19-time-based-greeting/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yajana Rao"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8d19639a-4cde-5d98-be08-d1767d919c0e","excerpt":"Time based user greetings (Good Morning, Afternoon, Evening) using moment.js Reference","html":"<h3>Time based user greetings (Good Morning, Afternoon, Evening) using moment.js</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function-variable function\">getGreetingTime</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">currentTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>currentTime <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>currentTime<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isValid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> splitAfternoon <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 24hr time to split the afternoon</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> splitEvening <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">17</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 24hr time to split the evening</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> currentHour <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentTime<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"HH\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentHour <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> splitAfternoon <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> currentHour <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> splitEvening<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Between 12 PM and 5PM</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Good afternoon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentHour <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> splitEvening<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Between 5PM and Midnight</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Good evening\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Between dawn and noon</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Good morning\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/AllanPooley/c41f2e4a0e63e3eaf89b57f2570fcb55\">Reference</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Greet user based on time of the day","date":null,"description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/technical/2020-07-19-time-based-greeting/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/sdlc/2020-08-16-sdlc-introduction/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Software Development Lifecycle Introduction"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/sdlc/2020-08-17-sdlc-models/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"SDLC Models"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1246554614","1250528154","280171546","2841359383"]}